quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  27,83,"Ne inyanga yakhulikhung’asia buli Abandu emikanda chiabalia abayingasinjia ebimanyisio biefu, ne baliemibwa ebituche ebituche"
  27,84,"Okhula shingala baliula mana (Nyasaye) aboole mbu: “koo enywe mwayingana ebimanyisio bianje nimulabimanyile obulayi tawe, nohomba nishina shiamwakholanga?.”"
  27,85,"Mana likhuwa nilibakwila khumabii kabakhola, ne baliwulela tsi"
  27,86,"Koo, shibalolangakhwo mbu efwe khwakhola eshilo okhuba shiokhwihotselesiamwo, nende eshitere okhubakhonya okhulola. Toto mu ako khulimwo nende ameeko khubandu basuubilanga"
  27,87,"Ne inyanga yolwika lulikhupwa, mana bibeyebeye bioosi ebili mwikulu nende khushialo halali ulia wa Nyasaye alichama, ne boosi bakhamwitsile nibali abateshele"
  27,88,"Ne olilola tsingulu nopara mbu tsiemele natsio tsichendanga shinga amaleesi. Nibo obwiranyi bwa Nyasaye, obwayakasilia obulayi buli eshindu, toto ye amanyile muno akamukholanga"
  27,89,"Abaliitsa namalayi balinyoola amalayi muno okhushilakhwo ako, nabo khushibeyibeyi shieyinyanga eyo baliba nomulembe"
  27,90,"Ne abalitsa nende amabii, obweni bwabu bulisindikhwa mumulilo (mana boboolelwe mbu) “shimurungungwa tawe halali kalia akamwakholanga.”"
  27,91,"Toto elomesibwe okhulaama Nyasaye omulesi welitokho lino eliahebwa oluyali, ne buli eshindu ni eshishie ne elomesibwe okhuba mubasalamu"
  27,92,"Ne osoome Ikurani , kho ulia ulunjikha alunjikhanga khulwa ye omwene, ne ulia ukora boola mbu: “ toto esie endisa mubekanyilisi.”"
  27,93,"Ne boola Mbu: “oluyali lwosi ni lwa Nyasaye yetsa okhubechesia ebimanyisio bibie mwitsa okhubimanya, ne Nyasaye shang’ang’alinga kamukholanga tawe.”"